The paper discusses the performance analysis of inband full-duplex D2D communications for wireless video distribution, which involves topics related to network infrastructure (NI), information theory (IT), multimedia (MM), systems and control (SY), and cryptography and security (CR). However, since the focus is on wireless communication and network performance, cs.NI is the most likely sub-category. The other sub-categories are also relevant due to the use of stochastic geometry, outage probability, and SI cancellation, which are common topics in these areas.
